<% content_for :title, "jwt-pq" %>

<section class="space-y-6">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Post-quantum JWT for Ruby</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
    jwt-pq adds ML-DSA (FIPS 204) signatures to the Ruby JWT ecosystem, plus an optional
    hybrid EdDSA + ML-DSA mode for defense-in-depth against both classical and quantum
    adversaries.
  </p>
  <p>
    Paste a token into the <%= link_to "debugger", debugger_path, class: "underline" %>,
    read the <%= link_to "quick start", quickstart_path, class: "underline" %>,
    or fetch the live JWKS at <code>/.well-known/jwks.json</code>.
  </p>
</section>
